[24/01/2018 07:02:11] <font color="#0000ff">(Música)</font>
[24/01/2018 07:02:15] <font color="#00ff00">Como el grunge de Nirvana,</font>
[24/01/2018 07:02:15] <font color="#00ff00">Pearl Jam o Alice in Chains,</font>
[24/01/2018 07:02:19] <font color="#00ff00">el pickleball nace en Seattle</font>
