[24/01/2018 11:21:26] <font color="#00ffff">del doctor Karl.</font>
[24/01/2018 11:21:27] <font color="#ffff00">Sí.</font>
[24/01/2018 11:21:30] <font color="#00ffff">Y entonces entras tú</font>
[24/01/2018 11:21:30] <font color="#00ffff">y juegas tu baza.</font>
