[24/01/2018 14:01:27] <font color="#ff00ff">¡Stan Ross!</font>
[24/01/2018 14:01:30] <font color="#ff00ff">¿Dónde estás?</font>
[24/01/2018 14:01:43] <font color="#ff00ff">¡Cobarde!</font>
