[24/01/2018 14:14:38] <font color="#ffffff">"HALLOUMI, SEMILLAS DE MANAZANA</font>
[24/01/2018 14:14:38] <font color="#ffffff">Y MASA MADRE"</font>
[24/01/2018 14:14:41] <font color="#00ffff">"Es un queso que rechina</font>
[24/01/2018 14:14:41] <font color="#00ffff">y parece plástico.</font>
