[24/01/2018 14:16:43] <font color="#00ffff">No de vaca.</font>
[24/01/2018 14:16:44] <font color="#ffffff">Exacto.</font>
[24/01/2018 14:16:44] <font color="#00ffff">¿Podemos echar un vistazo?</font>
[24/01/2018 14:16:45] <font color="#ffffff">Vamos.</font>
